org.jinq.jpa.transform

Class JPQLQueryTransform

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jinq.jpa.transform.JPQLQueryTransform
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JPQLGroupingMultiLambdaQueryTransform, JPQLMultiLambdaQueryTransform, JPQLNoLambdaQueryTransform, JPQLOneLambdaQueryTransform, OuterJoinOnTransform

    public abstract class JPQLQueryTransform
extends Object
    Subclasses of this class are used to hold the logic for applying a lambda to a JPQL query (e.g. how to apply a where lambda to a JPQL query, producing a new JPQL query)
